{"tid":2511450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Jeff Bezos投訴有效 NASA暫時擱置SpaceX 29億美元登月合約","createTime":"2021-05-01T02:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T05:46:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"4e283289536a4d2a143469ce78a09e8d1860f4ac","tid":2511450,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T02:34:57.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國太空總署NASA「阿提米絲」計畫（Artemis Program）日前宣布由SpaceX獲得29億美元（約新台幣826億元）登月船建造合約，消息一出引發競爭對手藍色起源及科技公司Dynetics抗議，NASA遂先行擱置合約，待監管單位釐清。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，美國政府問責署將針對兩家公司提出的抗議進行調查，意味著SpaceX無法第一時間拿到經費，也沒辦法和NASA展開初步會談。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\nNASA發言人聲明指出，「依照問責署提出的異議，NASA與SpaceX的人類登陸系統（HLS）合約進度暫停，直到問責署釐清所有和這筆合約有關的訴訟爭議。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3517394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3517394&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=ae9073f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3517394&h=ae23a265\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3517394</a>"},{"pid":"3326331d41347fc069860c71ad446876e9abb587","tid":2511450,"uid":191926,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"前幾日係twitter&nbsp;幾日前笑鳩人&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n點知人地真係玩法律手段&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e127fb65f016f1d3056fa5524c389bd333eafc98","tid":2511450,"uid":36134,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T02:40:10.000Z","msg":"咁樣隨時拖幾年<br />\n光頭佬真係賤到無人有"},{"pid":"c581245160ed67a77aa490addcae83847005e0ec","tid":2511450,"uid":40615,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"光頭佬正仆街"},{"pid":"84844dd4594c3e0003e7b1a56c5d69b74728e9bd","tid":2511450,"uid":191926,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e127fb65f016f1d3056fa55